column5: Had all the chores done by 9. What else to do with myself but go fishing.  Wound up being a beautiful day, except for the bluebird, wind less skies.  Lots of dink perch around, but the main event today were cats. Nothing to compare with the monsters on the Grand, but a lot of fun on lighter line.
Anyone that doesn't like Catfish... sux!!!
Certainly lots of fun catching them cats on light gear Thanks for sharing Bruce Jacques
Thanks for the post and pics Bruce, those cats are a lot of fun on ultralite gear.
Some great looking Channels and is that last one a decent Brown Bullhead?  Nice work
